# Risk Assessment Framework (High-Level)

## 1. Technical Risks
- Overfitting of interaction patterns
- Misclassification of user state
- Latency in reasoning module  

## 2. User Risks
- Over-reliance on suggestions  
- Misinterpretation of adaptive signals  
- Elevated expectations beyond scope  

## 3. Ethical Risks
- Unintended nudging  
- Ambiguous framing  
- Context misalignment  

## 4. Mitigation
- Clear boundaries  
- Built-in safety responses  
- Human-in-the-loop escalation  
